response.overview: Section 31 Alpha Squad is a covert unit of the secret Starfleet division Section 31 from the Star Trek universe, operating in the early 24th century. Led by Alok Sahar, the squad consisted of agents like Philippa Georgiou, Melle, Quasi, Zeph, Rachel Garrett, and Fuzz. Their mission was to stop a bioweapon called the Godsend, which originated from the mirror universe, but the team was compromised by a mole.
response.title: Section 31 Alpha Squad
